OL,3,CDrug producer jailed after property
OL,4,C'significantly hotter than neighbours'
OL,6,FA man who grew more than 400 cannabis
OL,7,Fplants in his home has been jailed
OL,8,Fafter police became suspicious of the
OL,9,Fhigh level of heat coming from his
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,FOfficers discovered that the property
OL,13,Fin Firemans Row, Sutton-in-Ashfield
OL,14,Fwas significantly hotter than
OL,15,Fneighbouring houses.
OL,17,FAfter further investigation they
OL,18,Fnoticed a man acting suspiciously
OL,19,Finside, and various items associated
OL,20,Fwith cannabis cultivation outside.
