OL,3,CDrug producer jailed after property
OL,4,C'significantly hotter than neighbours'
OL,6,FAfter forcing entry to the address on
OL,7,Fthe evening of 23 February this year,
OL,8,Fthe source of the excess heat was
OL,9,Fclear - more than 400 cannabis plants
OL,10,Fgrowing in multiple rooms in the semi-
OL,11,Fdetached property.
OL,13,FDori Sado, aged 38, was found hiding
OL,14,Fin the loft and was arrested at the
OL,15,Fscene.
OL,17,FSado, formerly of Firemans Row, Sutton-
OL,18,Fin-Ashfield, later pleaded guilty to
OL,19,Fproducing cannabis.
