OL,4,C'significantly hotter than neighbours'
OL,6,FAppearing at Nottingham Crown Court on
OL,7,FFriday (May 31) he was jailed for 12
OL,8,Fmonths.
OL,10,FA closure order was secured on the
OL,11,Faddress to prevent anyone else from
OL,12,Foccupying it for at least three months.
OL,14,FDetective Sergeant Clint Gloyn, of
OL,15,FNottinghamshire Police, said:
OL,17,F"Cannabis grows of this nature are a
OL,18,Fmajor fire risk and pose a significant
OL,19,Fdanger to neighbouring properties.
